data.description: Charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with an open floor plan. Open and bright with large living area and breakfast nook off of the kitchen. Kitchen features custom cabinets, granite counter tops, and stainless appliances. Ceramic tile in wet areas, and wood floors in the living room. Master suite includes a double wide shower, 2 sinks, and a large walk-in closet. Well-maintained lawn and landscape with a stained privacy fence that surrounds the secluded backyard.
